<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>


<p>This privacy policy describes how the College Database Management System (DBMS) collects, uses, and shares your personal information.</p>
<p>The College DBMS collects your personal information when you:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Create an account</li>
    <li>Submit a question or request</li>
    <li>Participate in a survey</li>
</ul>
<p>The College DBMS uses your personal information to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Provide you with the services you request</li>
    <li>Communicate with you about your account or the services we offer</li>
    <li>Improve our services</li>
</ul>
<p>The College DBMS shares your personal information with third-party vendors who help us provide our services, such as:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Hosting providers</li>
    <li>Email marketing providers</li>
    <li>Survey platforms</li>
</ul>
<p>The College DBMS may also share your personal information if required to do so by law or if we believe that sharing is necessary to protect our rights or the rights of others.</p>
<p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. You can also request that we stop processing your personal information. To exercise these rights, please contact us at vaznigeldwayne@gmail.com.</p>
<p>The College DBMS may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on our website.</p>
